      "id": "680ce14539a7aea3a06627d9",
      "text": "基底",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1745674572,
      "updated": 1745674572
    },
    {
      "id": "680ce166000000000032a3a4",
      "text": "[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/基底_(線型代数学) 基底 (線型代数学) - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1745674598,
      "updated": 1745674600
    },
    {
      "id": "680ce168000000000032a3a5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1745674600,
      "updated": 1745674600
    },
    {
      "id": "680ce173000000000032a3a6",
      "text": "体 [$ F] 上の[線型空間] [$ V] の[基底] [$ B] とは、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1745674610,
      "updated": 1745674791
    },
    {
      "id": "680ce227000000000032a3ae",
      "text": " [$ V] の[線型独立]な[部分集合]で、[$ V] を張る（生成する）ものを言う",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1745674791,
      "updated": 1745674792
    },
    {
      "id": "680ce14a000000000032a3a2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1745674572,
      "updated": 1745674647
    },
    {
      "id": "680ce1a2000000000032a3a7",
      "text": "[$ V]の[$ n]個のベクトルの集合[$ B = {\\bm v_1, …, \\bm v_n}]（または列[$ B=(\\bm v_1, …, \\bm v_n)]）が以下の条件を満たす時に[基底]になる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1745674658,
      "updated": 1745674783
    },
    {
      "id": "680ce1a3000000000032a3aa",
      "text": " [線型独立性]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1745674659,
      "updated": 1745674722
    },
    {
      "id": "680ce1a3000000000032a3ab",
      "text": "  [$ a_1, …, a_n ∈ F] に対して [$ a_1\\bm v_1 + … + a_n\\bm v_n = \\bm 0] が成り立つならば、[$ a_1 = … = a_n = 0] でなければならない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1745674659,
      "updated": 1745674803
    },
    {
      "id": "680ce1a3000000000032a3ac",
      "text": " [全域性]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1745674659,
      "updated": 1745674727
    },
    {
      "id": "680ce1a3000000000032a3ad",
      "text": "  [$ V] のどんな元 [$ \\bm x] も、適当な [$ a_1, …, a_n ∈ F] を選んで [$ \\bm x = a_1\\bm v_1 + … + a_n\\bm v_n] が成り立つようにできる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1745674659,
      "updated": 1745674860
    },
    {
      "id": "680ce1a3000000000032a3a8",
